+// mint a fresh IAM token per run via the federated-credentials flow — so the
+// lock is never actually taken. We replace the native binding with no-ops that
+// preserve the module's export surface and constant values, keeping the require
+// graph intact without shipping a platform-specific binary.
+// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
